short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows the latest release version right next to the name on a GitHub repository page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sometimes you want to quickly see which is the current release version of the project you are viewing. This extension shows the version of the latest release next to the name on a GitHub repository page.
